# Core Engine vs Content Pack (Amendment A4)

Before adding code, ask: **Core capability or country content?**

## Core (`@spike-life/domain`, `@spike-life/application`)

- FNA calculation, recommendations, decisions, consequences, life score
- Board movement, turns, dice, phases (no financial math on board)
- `Money` amounts in numeric form; currency code as data

## Content (`@spike-life/content-philippines`, future packs)

- Encounters, life situations, career paths, institutions (SSS, PhilHealth, Pag-IBIG, BIR)
- Currency/locale config, UI strings, archetype starting profiles
- Board JSON for a regional edition

## Never

- Hardcode `₱`, Philippine institutions, or Filipino-only events in domain services
- Put FNA formulas in content JSON

## Default MVP pack

Import from `@spike-life/content-philippines` in application/bootstrap — not from domain.
